  22 Feb 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> kdeconnect-0.7.3.ebuild,
  kdeconnect-0.8.ebuild:
  Update dependency on QCA plugins to use USE flags on app-crypt/qca:2
  unconditionally, to provide a single sane path for dependency resolution. Bug
  #541066.

*kdeconnect-0.8 (21 Feb 2015)

  21 Feb 2015; Michael Palimaka <kensington@gentoo.org> +kdeconnect-0.8.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  02 Feb 2015; Michael Palimaka <kensington@gentoo.org> kdeconnect-0.7.3.ebuild:
  Drop net-dns/avahi dependency which is no longer needed wrt bug #538166.

  28 Jan 2015; Michael Palimaka <kensington@gentoo.org> kdeconnect-0.7.3.ebuild:
  Adjust app-crypt/qca dependencies to handle merged plugins wrt bug #537640.

  22 Nov 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> -kdeconnect-0.7.2.ebuild:
  Cleanup old.

  15 Oct 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> kdeconnect-0.7.3.ebuild:
  Add missing dep on libfakekey. Fixes bug #525518.

